      "content": "the heating pad sounds okay but i'm really worried it's more than just gas because it's quite a sharp, stabbing feeling. i don't really want to go to the hospital or anything right now, it's so expensive and a hassle. if i just take a couple of codeine pills it'll hopefully just dull the edge so i can sleep through it? it isn't like it's an emergency if it's just cramps, right? i just need to get through the night.",
